&lt;/div>&lt;p>We don&amp;rsquo;t need to receive the packet, we just need to send it over the IPSEC tunnel, and it doesn&amp;rsquo;t matter after that.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>But write this, have it run continuosly in the background, and eventually you can catch in GDB:&lt;/p>
